      "name": "Medya",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/03/237301566/0b8e2c5d18b254a94b1f0e4157af1cdb_234079531504527699.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "April 1, 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "\"Either way... that book belongs in the hands of a bona fide scholar.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Although this book is pretty good, I didn't expect lectors to like this kind of story...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/237301566/cadd5559d2a5c1c3f4a4ce3d96e15ef9_4330869853506093995.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "September 17, 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "\"Only when a night as dark as the abyss descends, can one notice the luminous glimmer that has always been with them.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/23/237301566/92d7c1f6108b39f1f010dbb563ad188f_7328193714011362612.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "March 14, 2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Judging from your expression... you haven't forgotten me, have you?",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "What do you mean by \"Abyss Lectors all look the same, come back in human form\"? ...It seems the farewell gift I gave you at our last parting failed to leave a strong enough impression.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "I even went out of my way to pick some lovely flowers for you this time. But our Highness knows not of my coming, so I can't help you pass on any messages.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "So, do you think you can forgive me at last? Oh, come now! Lower your weapon and let's talk this over...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
